          <div class="page-header">
            <h1 id="terms">Terms of Service</h1>
          </div>
          <div class="full_width">
            <h3>What can you do with your website?</h3>
            <p>Anything that is not harmful, illegal, or malicious!</p>
            <p>Websites that are built on the SiteRubix.com domain are prohibited from doing anything illegal, delivering harmful or hurtful content, and cannot be used to perform any malicioius activity. Pornography or adult content is strictly prohibited and may be deleted anytime without notice.</p>
<p>We hold full control over disabling a website that violates any of the above, and have full descretion on any other issue that may be unforseen or covered directly within these terms of service.</p>
            <p>Building beautiful websites that are legal, and that do not harm anyone or anything are absolutely allowed and encouraged!</p>
            <h3>WealthyAffiliate.com</h3>
            <p>SiteRubix is part of the WealthyAffiliate.com Internet Entrepreneur community and requires a free Starter Account. All SiteRubix websites require the owner to have an account at Wealthy Affiliate and be in good standing. Any violations of the SiteRubix or WealthyAffiliate..com terms of service may result in the disabling of one's websites and removal of your account. Regardless of what &quot;type&quot; of account is held, we reserve the ability to act in good faith and protect our network from anything we deem that violates our terms of service.</p>
There are absolutely no obligations to users of WealthyAffiliate.com or SiteRubix to continue with the service and an account may be closed by the user by discontinuing to use the service.
<h3>Hosting &amp; Web Space</h3>
            <p>Hosting a website at SiteRubix.com is limited and at any time a website is not being actively used or updated we reserve the ability to remove that website from our servers to make room for other websites.</p>
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
